Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会遍体鳞伤之类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你遍体鳞伤的时候读了那本书再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.73,0:11:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起金八更喜欢仙八的女仆发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确得令人可恨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遍体鳞伤再说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐我放这了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西谁都不肯收拾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了之后该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:29.10,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望空太的愿望能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太的愿望…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是常说笑在脸 哭在心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:43.52,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也是 一旦有什么不顺心了 表面上会温柔地笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:47.14,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上内心是有着痛苦回忆的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学后的打工我请假… 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:13:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我放假了 一起去找猫的饲主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 总是麻烦你了 青山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小希和小光走了之后就差不多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么没关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为看着神田君我… 看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神田君…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…请问找我有什么事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢甜的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:14:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢甜的东西和咸的东西的混合物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名小姐怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很失落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油菜花庄？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名小姐画画能力堪称完美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱点只有故事剧情方面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我就让她把在樱花庄发生的事当作想象素材
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和椎名的立场反了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别说话 继续看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法自主选内裤的少年却有着明确的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方则是找不到目标的女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了各种事之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全称不上是Happy End 烂尾感很强的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这便是椎名小姐落选的最大理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开油菜花庄…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过很多次要她重画结局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那孩子一点都听不进去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说“因为那是空太的愿望”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当青春奔跑起来 力量就会涌出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话应该搞得定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 神田 忘了东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先得从这里开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹哪样啊这是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:16.37,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(520,550,520,320)}水明艺术大学 传媒学部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名小姐你觉得这样就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该把自己希望的结局画上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望的结局…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望的结局是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望可不是什么想离开樱花庄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是擅自给自己压力 想从樱花庄 从现实中逃避罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把升学调查表交了上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备升学到传媒学部去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后开始游戏的制作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:43.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还准备去挑战企划甄选
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为游戏制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就很感兴趣了 但是很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到失败的情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:18:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拿出浪费时间 害怕受伤这些净是不想做的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃去努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 看到椎名之后 开始有了改变的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望有一天也能像你这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又通宵作画了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是留在油菜花庄…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是椎名所想的真Happy End？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我接…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太帮我接…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 这是椎名的手机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才谢谢您了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名 椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起来 椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出道决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 是你的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人奖虽然没拿到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你的原稿修改之后能登在下个月月刊上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你也改好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很高兴 眼泪却流了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得好好庆祝你出道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我有一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个真不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:21:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没叫过女生的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对美咲不是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千寻也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是亚马逊战士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不公平了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫩 太嫩了 空太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是青春呢 小鹿乱撞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我都微微出汗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:38.48,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等… 你们从什么时候开始听的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:42.03,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就在了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:45.16,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 什么啦 快说快说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是还有话对我们说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:50.51,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点 别害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把心里话都说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:22:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 打扰你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.49,0:22:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我再次…回到樱花庄！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白恭喜你出道 and 学弟欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将平淡无奇怪罪于某人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.17,0:22:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…那是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.69,0:22:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那个想法 世界一瞬间就会改变颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.63,0:22:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花庄里被很多种颜色搞得乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:43.21,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(910,146)\frz356.858}空太大人\N应该感谢龙之介大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.99,0:22:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些在今后永远都不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:58.68,Title02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\fad(800,0)\pos(1002,174)\c&H7B7DE9&}#04 变色的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光是雌的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:49.86,Title01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(676,458)\3c&HD8D57D&}#05 樱花庄里认真的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种雌性会增加的预感 小光如此说道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一回目　殴れて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:52.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}二回目って　どうだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:59.54,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}偶然じゃないよね　三回目が遭うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:03.09,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}変わった人だと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:06.60,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}割と皆いうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:13.75,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}気になったことは 違うんだ　そこじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:20.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}君は多分純粋で　純粋を負けず
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:27.65,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}だから小さな日常にさえ　立ち向かって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:34.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}夢を持ってきた言葉じゃ　足りない夢にありが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:38.36,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}きっとこんな風に始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.91,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}新しいトキメキ世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.94,0:03:49.02,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}夢を持ってきた言葉を　知らないふりして行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:53.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}トキメキと夢のありか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}第一回 被人殴打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:52.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}第二回又会如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:59.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}会有第三回绝对不是偶然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:03.09,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}真是个怪人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:06.60,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}大家好像都这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:13.75,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}应该在意的事不是那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:20.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}你或许非常单纯 并且不向单纯低头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:27.65,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}所以即便是简单的日常也会抵抗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:34.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}充满着梦想的话语便是梦想不足的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:38.36,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一定是像这样开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.91,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}那片崭新的心跳世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.94,0:03:49.02,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}充满着梦想的话语 就当作没有听过继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:53.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}走向那心跳与梦的所在
